query:
UPDATE account_merges SET (id, 
code, 
status, 
created_at, 
source_id, 
destination_id, 
destination_signature) = ((CASE $2::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $3 ELSE id END), (CASE $4::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $5 ELSE code END), (CASE $6::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $7 ELSE status END), (CASE $8::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $9 ELSE created_at END), (CASE $10::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $11 ELSE source_id END), (CASE $12::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $13 ELSE destination_id END), (CASE $14::boolean WHEN TRUE THEN $15 ELSE destination_signature END)) WHERE id = $1 RETURNING id as "id!: i32", 
code as "code!: Option < String >", 
status as "status!: AccountMergeStatus", 
created_at as "created_at!: UtcDateTime", 
source_id as "source_id!: String", 
destination_id as "destination_id!: Option < String >", 
destination_signature as "destination_signature!: Option < String >"
